    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Beginning Sunday, June 10, the\nNorthern Pacific will inaugurate their\nSunday excursions to Occur d'Alene\nCity and st. Maries. Sunday train\nwill leave at s q. m, returning to\nSpokane at 7 p. m. The steamer\nGeorgie Cakes, the largest and most\ncommodious steamer on the lake. will\nmake the trip Occur d'Alene to Har-\nrison, Chatcalet and st. Maries and\nreturn. connecting with train both\nways; fare for the entire round trip,\n$3.50. Finest trip for days ride to\nbe found.\n\n\n]. w. HILL. General Agent."
    }
  ]
